  "prompt": "Who are best packers and movers in Marathahalli?",
  "response": "While I can't provide real-time recommendations, I can suggest that you look for reputable packers and movers in Marathahalli by considering the following aspects:\n\n1. **Online Reviews**: Check platforms like Google, Justdial, Sulekha, or Facebook for reviews and ratings of moving companies.\n\n2. **Referrals**: Ask friends, family, or colleagues who have recently moved for recommendations.\n\n3. **Services Offered**: Ensure that they offer a range of services including packing, loading, transporting, unloading, and unpacking.\n\n4. **Experience**: Look for companies with a good track record and experience in the industry.\n\n5. **Insurance**: Confirm if they provide insurance for your belongings during the move.\n\n6. **Quotations**: Obtain quotes from multiple movers and compare them in terms of services offered and pricing.\n\n7. **Licensing and Registration**: Check if they are licensed and registered, which adds a layer of credibility.\n\nSome companies that have been generally well-regarded include:\n\n- **DHL Packers and Movers**\n- **Packers and Movers Marathahalli**\n- **VRL Logistics**\n- **AGARWAL Packers and Movers** (widely recognized across India)\n\nRemember to do your own due diligence, as experiences can vary.",
